other.name: :question: Other Category
other.desc: A category with commands that don't belong in other categories. You can type `.help <command>` to get some more detailed info on a command!

image.name: :camera: Image Category
image.desc: A command category consisting of image manipulation commands. You can type `.help <command>` to get some more detailed info on a command!

moderation.name: :hammer: Moderation Category
moderation.desc: A command category consisting of moderation related commands. You can type `.help <command>` to get some more detailed info on a command!

weather.name: Weather
weather.desc: Sends you some weather related information about a city!

serverinfo.name: Server info
serverinfo.desc: Sends some information about the server!

vote.name: Vote
vote.desc: Sends a link to vote for the bot!

fromhex.name: From Hex
fromhex.desc: Converts hexadecimal code to ascii characters.

frombinary.name: From Binary
frombinary.desc: Converts binary code to ascii characters.

cat.name: Cat
cat.desc: Sends a random picture of a cat.

dog.name: Dog
dog.desc: Sends a random picture of a dog.

comrade.name: Comrade
comrade.desc: Adds a soviet overlay to your profile picture.

blur.name: Blur
blur.desc: Sends a blurred version of your profile picture.

waifuai.name: Waifu AI
waifuai.desc: Sends an AI generated anime girl.

userinfo.name: User Info
userinfo.desc: Sends some information about the mentioned user!

support.name: Support
support.desc: Invites you to the support server.

yoda.name: Yoda
yoda.desc: Translates your message to Yoda's language.

yomomma.name: Yo Momma
yomomma.desc: Sends a random yo momma joke.

nitro.name: Nitro
nitro.desc: Sends you a link to claim your free Discord Nitro!

iamspeed.name: I Am Speed
iamspeed.desc: Generates an I am speed meme with your profile picture!

water.name: Water
water.desc: Generates a water meme with your text!

mind.name: Change My Mind
mind.desc: Generates a change my mind meme with your text!

uwufy.name: Uwufy
uwufy.desc: Sends an uwufied version of your message.

invite.name: Invite
invite.desc: Sends a link allowing you to invite Donut to your own server!

avatar.name: Avatar
avatar.desc: Sends the avatar of the mentioned user!

car.name: Car
car.desc: Generates a car meme with your text!

missionpassed.name: Mission Passed
missionpassed.desc: Adds a mission passed overlay to your profile picture

wasted.name: Wasted
wasted.desc: Adds a wasted text to a mentioned user's profile picture.

simpcard.name: Simpcard
simpcard.desc: Creates a simpcard for the given user.

ironic.name: Ironic
ironic.desc: Sends your message but with randomly generated capital letters.

clear.name: Clear
clear.desc: Deletes a given amount of messages!

lockdown.name: Lockdown
lockdown.desc: A command used to lock a channel (make people unable to type).

help.name: Help
help.desc: Sends you info on a given command.

eject.name: Eject
eject.desc: Generates an Among Us like ejected screen.

hug.name: Hug
hug.desc: A command that lets you hug someone!

triggered.name: Triggered
triggered.desc: Sends a triggered version of your profile picture.
